Judges have been known throughout time as the Judges of Darkness.  
When mortal justice isn't enough for a victim they seek another 
spiritual justice. The Judges of Darkness only seek out to destroy  
those who have done the innocent wrong. Only when someone has  
fallen, and are a spirit, may they call the power of a Judge to 
settle the situation. Senseless killing is not part of the Judges  
of Darkness. Although they do must look out for the Mediums; those  
which feel that the person being judged should have a fair trial  
in front of the Ten Demon Kings. They have been seen to wear a  
long flowing cloaks along with magical golden jewelry and black  
lipstick. They definately pose a threat to all those that defy  
the power of the spritual world and those who dishonor the  
living with their selfish ways. 
